snippet.title: Will You Ever Return: In da Hood
snippet.description:
play the game here: http://gamejolt.com/games/rpg/will-yo...
Support me here: http://flottantpigbit.blogspot.com/
lyrics:
 1987, muthafuckin Philly
Fuckin city of Brotherly lOve
this is fresh

Here's a fucking story all about how
My life got fucking turned upside down
I'd like to take a minute
Fucking sit right there,
I'll tell you how I became the prince of a town called Bel Air.

West fucking Philly, born and raised.
On the muthafucking playground I spent my days
Smoking all the blunts, relaxin' all cool
And all shootin some heroin outside of school
When a couple of punks fucking up to no good
Started fucking around in my neighborhood
I got in one little ruckus, my momma got scared
She said 'You're a stupid mother fucker, get the fuck out of here'
